---
id: Return_Format
title: Return Format
sidebar_label: Return Format
---

All interfaces’ returns are in JSON format.

## 请求参数

| Name   | Type | Mandatory | Default | Description |
| ------ | ---- | --------- | ------- | ----------- |
| `None` |      | No        |         |             |

## 响应示例

```json
{
    "returnCode": 200,
    "result": {
        "serverTime": 1636612706739
    },
    "msgInfo": "Success."
    "error": null,
}
```
